ed="T" n="0865c20"/><persName key="A013559">釋三刀<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>者，本姓<name>曹</name>，<placeName key="PL000000019383">廬陵</placeName>人也<ptr target="#n684"/>。天然之性，<lb
ed="T" n="0865c21"/>嗜於蔬食。羈貫<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1861"/>成童，志願出家。于時自<placeName key="PL000000000150">江</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0865c22"/>以西，從<persName key="A008454">安</persName><persName key="A010333">史</persName>之亂，南方不寧，多事土扶<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2001"/>，故強<lb
ed="T" n="0865c23"/>兼弱，兵革未休。<date key="j20033642003393" notAfter-iso="+0773-01-01" notBefore-iso="+0772-12-03"><name>大曆</name>七年十一月</date><ptr target="#n685"/>，<placeName key="PL000000030464">廣州</placeName><persName key="A013560">呂<roleName>大<lb
ed="T" n="0865c24"/>夫</roleName></persName>被翻城。<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>奉</sic><corr>承</corr></choice><ptr target="#n3040"/><placeName key="PL000000018628">洪州</placeName><persName key="A013561">路嗣恭</persName>牒<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2002"/><placeName key="PL000000019383">吉州</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0865sgsz11"/>刺<anchor xml:id="end0865sgsz11"/>史<persName key="A013562">劉<lb
ed="T" n="0865c25"/>寧</persName><ptr target="#n3039"/>徵兵三千人，同收<placeName key="PL000000030482">番禺</placeName>。法師舊名<persName key="A013559">伯連</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0865c26"/>其為人也強渥而貌惡，且心循良，恒持誦《金<lb
ed="T" n="0865c27"/>剛經》，以筒盛經，佩之于身，誓不婚娶。然不<lb
ed="T" n="0865c28"/>揚此善于他，惟密行愈至。無何<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g493"/>，被括為軍。<lb
ed="T" n="0865c29"/>呈閱之時，又選充行營小將，非其所好，遂<pb ed="T" n="0866a" xml:id="T50.2061.0866a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0866a01"/>亡命焉。時徵兵頗急，牒諸處要害捕逐。於<lb
ed="T" n="0866a02"/>本州<placeName key="PL000000056757">洋口</placeName>擒送<persName key="A013562">劉寧</persName>，令於<placeName key="PL000000055643">朱木橋</placeName>處死。三<lb
ed="T" n="0866a03"/>下刃俱折，<persName key="A013562">劉</persName>怪問之，遂言素志捨家，恒持<lb
ed="T" n="0866a04"/>經法，如斯怯懦，恐衂軍威，是以亡耳。問經<lb
ed="T" n="0866a05"/>何在？曰：「被獲時遺墜。」遂令搜取，果數百步<lb
ed="T" n="0866a06"/>外得之，竹筒有刃痕而幾絕。<persName key="A013562">劉</persName>拱手稱<anchor xml:id="beg0866sgsz1"/>歎<anchor xml:id="end0866sgsz1"/><lb
ed="T" n="0866a07"/>久之，乃縱其為僧。奏聞，勅下本道號<persName key="A013559">三刀<lb
ed="T" n="0866a08"/>法師</persName>，配本郡<placeName key="PL000000019365">龍興寺</placeName>。後加精進，卒于住<lb
ed="T" n="0866a09"/>所。</p>
